One Small Improvement You Can Add

When testing APIs, also document them.

Example:

GET /api/search?q=string
POST /api/music/upload
POST /api/music/album

------------------------------------
Small Bonus (VERY NICE)

Also add central error handler middleware.

Instead of writing try/catch everywhere.

Example:

app.use((err, req, res, next) => {
  res.status(err.status || 500).json({
    success: false,
    message: err.message
  });
});

